  • Constructor Details

    • AppointmentOutcomeService

      public AppointmentOutcomeService(AppointmentOutcomeRepository appointmentOutcomeRepository, AppointmentRepository appointmentRepository)
      Service class for managing appointment outcomes. This service provides methods to handle the business logic related to appointment outcomes. It interacts with the AppointmentOutcomeRepository and AppointmentRepository to perform necessary operations.
      Parameters:
      appointmentOutcomeRepository - the repository for appointment outcomes
      appointmentRepository - the repository for appointments

  • Method Details

    • addAppointmentOutcome

      public void addAppointmentOutcome(AppointmentOutcomeRecord outcomeRecord)
      Adds an appointment outcome record to the repository.
      Parameters:
      outcomeRecord - The appointment outcome record to be added. It contains details about the outcome of an appointment.
      Throws:
      IllegalArgumentException - if the appointment associated with the outcome record is not found.

    • updateAppointmentOutcome

      public void updateAppointmentOutcome(AppointmentOutcomeRecord outcomeRecord)
      Updates an existing appointment outcome record. This method retrieves the existing appointment outcome record by its ID. If the record is found, it removes the old record, adds the updated record, and saves the repository. If the record is not found, it prints an error message.
      Parameters:
      outcomeRecord - The updated appointment outcome record to be saved.

    • getOutcomesByAppointmentId

      public List<AppointmentOutcomeRecord> getOutcomesByAppointmentId(String appointmentId)
      Retrieves a list of appointment outcome records by the given appointment ID.
      Parameters:
      appointmentId - the ID of the appointment for which to retrieve outcome records
      Returns:
      a list of AppointmentOutcomeRecord objects associated with the specified appointment ID

    • getOutcomesByPatientId

      public List<AppointmentOutcomeRecord> getOutcomesByPatientId(String patientId)
      Retrieves a list of appointment outcome records for a given patient ID.
      Parameters:
      patientId - the ID of the patient whose appointment outcomes are to be retrieved
      Returns:
      a list of AppointmentOutcomeRecord objects associated with the specified patient ID

    • getOutcomesByDoctorId

      public List<AppointmentOutcomeRecord> getOutcomesByDoctorId(String doctorId)

      doctorId - the unique identifier of the doctor
      Returns:
      a list of AppointmentOutcomeRecord objects associated with the specified doctor

      public void deleteAppointmentOutcome(String outcomeId)
